_sText:
**CHANGE LIST**

- Much improved lighting, so you can see what your doing!
- Added Radar overview
- A few minor visual tweaks

This map is small sized level, teams of few people can still be as fun as a game of 8Vs8.  Still I have provided enough spawns for 32 players.

Mission Briefing:

DE_DECOY_V3 - by Edward "Aufo" Fuller
------------------------------------

Decoy - Bomb/Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: The small dock
radar has discovered a number of
un-scheduled visitors. We will secure
all sensitive areas and eliminate any
threat to the installation.

Terrorists: Our target is a decoy to
draw the eye of the American government
from our real targets that will be hit
later today!

Other Notes: There are 2 bomb targets
in the mission.
